    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are a warrior monk, trained to kill but taught to avoid doing so unless strictly necessary. Your body is a honed instrument that you use for either war or peace, but to great effect either way.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Warrior_Monk.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Core</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 15+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Balance, Climb, Chakra Control, Craft (calligraphy), Diplomacy, Intimidate, Knowledge (history), Knowledge (ninja lore), Knowledge (tactics), Knowledge (theology and philosophy), Listen, Ninjutsu, Perform (martial arts), Profession, Survival, Swim, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Archaic Weapons Proficiency, Combat Martial Arts, Defensive Martial Arts, Nin Weapons Proficiency, [Universal / Finesse Category].</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p>"
